<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,1808,2013]" lastBlockId="12.[151,1436,151,213]" lastPageId="12" lastPageNumber="313" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">
<bibRefCitation author="Samy" box="[199,344,1952,1976]" pageId="11" pageNumber="312" refString="Samy, O. (1972) Psyllids of Egypt (Homoptera: Psyllidae). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique d'Egypte, 56, 437 - 480." type="journal article" year="1972">Samy (1972)</bibRefCitation>
described the species in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Enderlein" authorityYear="1921" box="[620,785,1952,1977]" class="Insecta" family="Aphalaridae" genus="Craspedolepta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="312" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[620,785,1952,1977]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">Craspedolepta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. It has a small, very short, parallel-sided frons (rather than narrow, long, ribbon-shaped as in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Enderlein" authorityYear="1921" box="[530,695,1988,2013]" class="Insecta" family="Aphalaridae" genus="Craspedolepta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="312" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[530,695,1988,2013]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">Craspedolepta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) and a subrectangular, laterally rounded mesosternum (rather than narrowed in the middle, with antero-lateral rim as in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Enderlein" authorityYear="1921" box="[791,956,151,176]" class="Insecta" family="Aphalaridae" genus="Craspedolepta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="313" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[791,956,151,176]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="313">Craspedolepta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). Based on these characters, the species belongs to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Loginova" authorityYear="1964" box="[274,372,189,212]" class="Insecta" family="Aphalaridae" genus="Crastina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="313" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[274,372,189,212]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="313">Crastina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Here we formally transfer it as 
<taxonomicName authority="(Samy, 1972)" authorityName="Spodek &amp; Burckhardt &amp; Freidberg" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="Samy" baseAuthorityYear="1972" box="[735,1178,188,213]" class="Insecta" family="Aphalaridae" genus="Crastina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="313" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="heslopharrisoni" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis box="[735,1018,188,213]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="313">Crastina heslopharrisoni</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Samy" box="[1033,1170,188,212]" pageId="12" pageNumber="313" refString="Samy, O. (1972) Psyllids of Egypt (Homoptera: Psyllidae). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique d'Egypte, 56, 437 - 480." type="journal article" year="1972">Samy, 1972</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1189,1314,188,213]" pageId="12" pageNumber="313">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
